builder.model

Class BuilderModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • builder.model.BuilderModel

  • public class BuilderModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The Model stored by a BuilderView Boundary object. Contains information and references to a list of allLevels, as well as the current level being modified.
    Author:
    Nicholas Panzarino
